            "answer_text": "Bihar has a diverse culture with around 5 different dialects of different regions . Among them only bhojpuri has got so much of recognition unfortunately because of the item songs made in bhojpuri . However in the same language , u can get to hear beautiful collection of folk songs but it's only the item songs that have been publicised with vulgar content . People outside the state know bihari songs to be the ones as item songs only . So this may be the reason why bhojpuri is considered as low class language. ",
